<section id="introduction">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Hi, I'm Isabela Martins. I'm a Brazilian living in Scotland and a self-taught artist. I love to work with mixed textures, including plaster, resin, acrylics, acrylic inks, alcohol inks, and more. I draw my inspiration from nature, particularly the ocean. Blue is my muse, and I have a special affinity for all shades of blue. I also love earth tones and pastel colors, which you will find in my works.</p>
</section>

